    "system": {
      "description": {
        "value": "<h3>Tyrant of the Hex</h3>\n<p>While your Hex Aura is active, a creature affected by your Hexing Challenge cannot willingly move farther away from you unless it first succeeds on a Wisdom saving throw against your Warlock spell save DC.</p>\n<p>In addition, when a creature affected by your Hexing Challenge is reduced to 0 Hit Points inside your Hex Aura, you regain 1 expended Hex Charge. You can regain a Hex Charge this way no more than once per turn.</p>",
