      "description": {
        "value": "<h3>Shadow Marshal</h3>\n<p>When you use Hexbound Specter, you can summon two Hexbound Specters instead of one.</p>\n<p>When you issue a verbal command to one Hexbound Specter, you can issue the same command to any Hexbound Specters you control.</p>\n<p>No more than one Hexbound Specter can make a Life Drain attack on the same turn unless you spend 1 Hex Charge.</p>\n<p>If you roll Initiative and have no use of Hexbound Specter remaining, you can regain one use of Hexbound Specter by expending one use of Hex Aura.</p>",
